&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant in Anaesthetics - Critical Care (Allied Specialty)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;East Surrey Hospital&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full time - 10PA&#39;s&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;£82,096 - £110,683 per annum&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint a full time Consultant in Critical Care. This post is new and an exciting opportunity for a candidate from specialties allied to Critical Care to join our dynamic team. Job Plan details can be found within the job description.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are immensely proud of the trust&#39;s Outstanding status and the successful candidate will join a department that is friendly, engaged and provides excellent training and mentor support. The successful appointee will work as an integral part of the team and have equal access to junior staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal enquiries are welcomes by contacting Critical Care Lead Dr Claire Mearns claire.mearns@nhs.net or Clinical Lead Dr Ravi Kumar ravi.kumar3@nhs.net 01737 768511 ext. 6046&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Claire Mearns - Critical Care Lead (email: claire.mearns@nhs.net), telephone number: 01737 768 511 ext 6046&lt;/p&gt;
